      "summary": "Eric: After you log in, go to Inventory and then manage all inventory. And then you will see this listing. You need to convert it to a BM change to Fulfilled by Amazon. All right. Thank you.",
      "headline": "Eric: Go to Inventory and then manage all inventory. And then you will see this listing",
